# Custom revdiff keybindings — deltas applied on top of the defaults
# (revdiff loads Default() first, then these). Full template: revdiff --dump-keys
#
# Swap from defaults: brackets navigate annotations, parens navigate hunks.
# (The default { } still also jump annotations; left in place as aliases.)
map [ prev_annotation
map ] next_annotation
map ( prev_hunk
map ) next_hunk
